            "body": "For the record, same-site does not restrict 3rd party cookies. It does prevent the browser from sending the cookie to other domains than the current site:\r\n\r\n> Subsequent requests from that user agent can be expected to contain the following header field if and only if both the requested resource and the resource in the top-level browsing context match the cookie."
